dct_title_s: Map of the Shaktu Valley, north west frontier, Punjab from a sketch by Capt. G. F. Young, D.A. Qr. Mr. Genl
dct_description_sm: Actual, probable, and dry courses of rivers are shown. Author's route shown in red. Relief shown by hachures, spot heights, and text descriptions. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 4 (1882), no. 9, pp. 537-44; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
